Author: SofyaVolkova190
Text: I just don’t tell anyone because I don’t want them to force me to eat just because which I KNOW they’d do. I think I’ll just stick to “haha food is my life, I’m just naturally small”

Author: livipup
Text: I mostly don't want anyone to try to look like me or think being so thin is okay. I don't want their pity, but I also don't want their praise. :( It's kind of hard to practice body positivity while worrying about people's health though.
